    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just that \"letting go\" part you mentioned... it feels so much more peaceful than trying to keep trekking through things i don't care about anymore. like, if a traveler has seen the best parts, isn't there a certain dignity in just deciding the trip is over? instead of just wandering aimlessly until they're exhausted?",
